            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#TA">
                <ns0:p>To the Shades of the Underworld. Cornelia Soteris lived 85 years. Auctus, her brother, made this.</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="commentary">
                <ns0:p>ISic000161-000164 were all found together and, as Bivona notes, should all belong to the same family, since they share the same nomen (Cornelius) and the Auctus of <ns0:ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000161">ISic000161</ns0:ref> is the dedicant for his wife (<ns0:ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000163">ISic000163</ns0:ref>) and, in this text, his sister. The relationship of Cornelius Castor in <ns0:ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000162">ISic000162</ns0:ref> to the other three is not known (could be a son or grandson given the ages).</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
